%h2 Goals vs. Priorities
%p
  Your priorities can and do change over time. For example, you may go for years desperately trying to
  =@quad.ej.goal
  just to wake up one morning and discover that it’s no longer something that you need to worry so much about. Conversely, you may not be particularly worried about
  =@quad.ep.goal.ing
  for years, and then something changes and it’s your number one priority.   
%p
  Your goals, on the other hand, never change. If you suddenly decide, due to some unusual circumstances, that 
  =@quad.ep.realm.ej.goal.ing
  is something that you need or want to do, you don't have to set it as a new goal, you merely have to stop trying to
  =@quad.ep.goal
  and you will automagically
  =@quad.ep.realm.ej.goal.punctuate